::Shadow Wing::

She started walking again through the trees towards the Maximal base.  She 
stopped and looked at Lunarpine.
"I can make no promises save one.  If you join us in our cause, you have the 
honor of a true warrior.  This is all I can offer you."

She turned and started walking again towards the base.  She hoped he would 
consider what she had said and join them.  She thought he was extremely good 
looking for a bot.  But she also knew that once te other bots got a good 
look at him, her chances of anything where through.  But Oh well, she 
thought, that's life I guess.
